      <title>马约卡斯认为无人机威胁尚未迫在眉睫，呼吁赋予其更广泛的权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/mayorkas-sees-no-imminent-drone-threat-calls-for-wider-powers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国土安全部部长亚历杭德罗·马约卡斯表示，美国人可能会在夜空中看到更多的无人机，但没有证据表明外国参与或构成国家安全风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/mayorkas-sees-no-imminent-drone-threat-calls-for-wider-powers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 15:08:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登计划在最后阶段采取措施解决人工智能、赦免和土地问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/biden-plans-measures-on-ai-clemency-and-lands-in-final-stretch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据一份致盟友的备忘录，拜登总统计划在其政府任期的最后几周就土地保护、赦免和人工智能采取行动，以期在唐纳德·特朗普就职之前将自己的政治遗产编入法典。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-15/biden-plans-measures-on-ai-clemency-and-lands-in-final-stretch</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 15 Dec 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
